{"tid":2217111,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 laptop鍵盤支架一問","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T09:44:03.000Z","uid":318551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"acdda6afac1a1e43428efb5b27a1c846482ba17a","tid":2217111,"uid":318551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"我電腦係華碩laptop<br />\n當時手多 拆過個keyboard出嚟 <br />\n砌返落去就有啲掣鬆鬆地 好似要甩咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ii4ME1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fii4ME1T.jpg&h=6415a8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPS 對唔住係淘寶相 因為唔知呢舊嘢叫咩<br />\n懷疑自己就係整爛左圖中嘅支架<br />\n我想問有邊間舖頭可以幫我換呢啲支架呢<br />\n同埋大約幾多錢<br />\n最好就係黃店<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感激不盡"},{"pid":"c2ad808216aca7f5125bb156547c10d7e4c39783","tid":2217111,"uid":335003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"簡單解決方法 -  <br />\n配返個矽膠防塵貼，成個黐在keboard 面。一次過成塊黐住所有 key 即刻唔驚甩。 各大電腦商場 / 配件鋪有售<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要揾支架嘅話 -<br />\n淘佬，因為得支那先有呢啲顯碎嘢賣<br />\n一係人哋玩自組鍵盤嘅地方揾配件，不過呢啲唔平同通常要自己嚟。 之前好似見過有自組鍵盤post 教人邊度買。<br />\n<br />\nAlternatively, 去揾啲電腦醫生。問下價，佢哋通常會有啲部廢電腦做零件機拆出嚟。不過人哋都要收人工，唔平得去邊。"},{"pid":"89e4ffdf2d702fd1baeb9171e5d148d7eeb1c11c","tid":2217111,"uid":318551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ad808216aca7f5125bb156547c10d7e4c39783","tid":2217111,"uid":335003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"簡單解決方法 -  <br />\n配返個矽膠防塵貼，成個黐在keboard 面。一次過成塊黐住所有 key 即刻唔驚甩。 各大電腦商場 / 配件鋪有售<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要揾支架嘅話 -<br />\n淘佬，因為得支那先有呢啲顯碎嘢賣<br />\n一係人哋玩自組鍵盤嘅地方揾配件，不過呢啲唔平同通常要自己嚟。 之前好似見過有自組鍵盤post 教人邊度買。<br />\n<br />\nAlternatively, 去揾啲電腦醫生。問下價，佢哋通常會有啲部廢電腦做零件機拆出嚟。不過人哋都要收人工，唔平得去邊。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"感激<br />\n但有冇啲咩電腦醫生可以推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952689f2d8a570b0661ad292618996a9df39dc76","tid":2217111,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e4ffdf2d702fd1baeb9171e5d148d7eeb1c11c","tid":2217111,"uid":318551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ad808216aca7f5125bb156547c10d7e4c39783","tid":2217111,"uid":335003,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"簡單解決方法 -  <br />\n配返個矽膠防塵貼，成個黐在keboard 面。一次過成塊黐住所有 key 即刻唔驚甩。 各大電腦商場 / 配件鋪有售<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要揾支架嘅話 -<br />\n淘佬，因為得支那先有呢啲顯碎嘢賣<br />\n一係人哋玩自組鍵盤嘅地方揾配件，不過呢啲唔平同通常要自己嚟。 之前好似見過有自組鍵盤post 教人邊度買。<br />\n<br />\nAlternatively, 去揾啲電腦醫生。問下價，佢哋通常會有啲部廢電腦做零件機拆出嚟。不過人哋都要收人工，唔平得去邊。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"感激<br />\n但有冇啲咩電腦醫生可以推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:44:03.000Z","msg":"去福榮/新高登問下， 果頭多。<br />\n貪方便可以去屋邨電腦維修鋪問，不過預咗使錢買方便。"}]}